ref=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/crash_47\">Thomas Piron</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/spaceshipone\">Timoth√©e Brosille</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/timotheemoulin\">timotheemoulin</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/wolforg\">Didier Demory / Wolforg</a> et&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/byohann6\">Yohann Billard</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Si vous voulez en savoir plus sur les diff√©rentes mani√®res dont vous pouvez contribuer au d√©veloppement de WordPress, n&rsquo;h√©sitez pas √† consulter le <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core\">blog de d√©veloppement du c≈ìur WordPress</a>, ou les guides r√©alis√©s par la communaut√© francophone sur la <a href=\"https://fr.wordpress.org/team/handbook/\">traduction de WordPress</a> et la <a href=\"https://fr.wordpress.org/team/handbook/traduire-la-documentation-de-wordpress-en-francais/rejoindre-lequipe-de-traduction-de-la-documentation/\">traduction de la documentation de WP</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:64:\"https://fr.wordpress.org/2020/08/11/wordpress-5-5-eckstine/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:53:\"Les changements techniques √† venir sur WordPress 5.5\";s:7:\"attribs